00:03:59.550 --> 00:04:01.790
Not exactly 137.

00:04:01.790 --> 00:04:06.400
And lo and behold, 137 is a nice
Pythagorean prime, which

00:04:06.400 --> 00:04:09.330
I think is quite nice.

00:04:09.330 --> 00:04:12.470
And if we work that one out, of
course, we see-- how can we

00:04:12.470 --> 00:04:12.930
make it up?

00:04:12.930 --> 00:04:16.430
Well, with a little bit of
thinking, we can see that 11

00:04:16.430 --> 00:04:20.140
